1
00:00:07,636 --> 00:00:09,694
I will go on a walk.
我要去散步

2
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:12,370
I must wear warm things.
我必须穿上暖和的东西

3
00:00:13,032 --> 00:00:15,309
I walk and walk in the snow.
我在雪里走啊走

4
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:19,221
I hike up this tall, tall rock.
我爬上这块高高的石头

5
00:00:19,549 --> 00:00:23,825
I stop, sit, and look as far as I can.
我停下来   坐下   极目远眺

6
00:00:24,509 --> 00:00:27,236
From here I can spot a seal.
从这里我能发现一只海豹

7
00:00:27,563 --> 00:00:30,683
It is big, and its skin shines.
它很大   它的皮肤在发光

8
00:00:31,025 --> 00:00:32,283
It looks at me.
它看着我

9
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:36,356
From here I can spot the whales.
从这里我能发现鲸鱼们

10
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,981
The whales swim in the water.
鲸鱼们在水里游泳

11
00:00:39,309 --> 00:00:40,661
They look at me.
它们看着我

12
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:44,727
From this rock I can spot the birds.
从这块石头这里我能发现鸟儿们

13
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,560
The birds look up.
鸟儿们向上看

14
00:00:46,741 --> 00:00:48,872
They all look at me.
它们都看着我

15
00:00:50,065 --> 00:00:51,949
I can see the penguins.
我能看到企鹅们

16
00:00:52,145 --> 00:00:53,432
They walk tall.
他们昂首挺胸

17
00:00:53,890 --> 00:00:56,043
They all call and call.
它们都叫啊叫

18
00:00:57,025 --> 00:00:58,625
I call to them all,
我对它们喊

19
00:00:58,850 --> 00:01:02,843
"I like this place of ice, and I like all of you!"
我喜欢这个冰天雪地的地方   我喜欢你们

